## Proposed Changes

### Database

#### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///c:/dnyanesh/AI_Figma_UIUX_Design_Generator_Platform/server/prisma/schema.prisma)
Add a `GenerationHistory` model to store the history of prompts, classifications, and generated JSON schemas. Integrate it with the `User` model.

```prisma
model User {
  // Existing fields...
  exports   Export[]
  history   GenerationHistory[] // Added relation

  @@map("users")
}

model GenerationHistory {
  id             String   @id @default(uuid()) @db.Uuid
  userId         String   @map("user_id") @db.Uuid
  prompt         String
  classification Json?
  schema         Json
  createdAt      DateTime @default(now()) @map("created_at")
  user           User     @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([createdAt])
  @@map("generation_histories")
}
```

